name: Bet more
description: Bet more is an internet meme based on the mantra "Bet more and let it ride". The meme become popular among Crypto Twitter in 2017 based on its cultural significance and the high stakes/high rewards ecosphere of crypto. The bet more meme is a cultural mantra. The BET MORE token is a meme coin with no inherent value or financial expectations, and it is intended solely for entertainment purposes only.
